title: Integrate your private thoughts, your public thoughts, and others' (public) thoughts.
pid: d40ed7ac-7712-4493-8d25-3c3e306801ab
body: |2-
  You can keep all of them in view,
  as if they were part of the same document,
  without revealing your private notes.
  Public thoughts on love (by others and yourself)
  intermingled with your plans for Valentine's Day.
  Private hunches that might turn into research papers
  intermingled with public notes about science.
  Etc.
